title: ISic003676. I.Sicily inscription 003676
body:
Facsimile Images

1[---]SA·[---]
2[---]N·[---]

Apparatus criticus

Text as reported by Carettoni; Carettoni reports the top of a vertical stroke after the A
2: Carettoni reports the top of a downward right slanting stroke after what appears to be traces of the letter N

translation

commentary

The text is one of several fragments reported by Carettoni amongst material recovered from the multiple trenches along the so-called 'muro a bugnato', on the east side of the area of the agora. It has not been observed since, but should be in store on site

bibliography

  • Carettoni NSA 1961 303 no. 9b https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392
